0 1234567\n\u2022 We offer full refund or replacement for verified issues\n\u2022 Your feedback helps us improve our service'},{icon:'person-outline',title:'How to manage my account?',answer:'To manage your account:\n\u2022 Go to Profile screen from the main menu\n\u2022 Update profile picture, name, and email\n\u2022 Change password in Settings\n\u2022 View and manage saved addresses\n\u2022 Check order history\n\u2022 Update notification preferences'}].map((e,t)=>(0,l.jsx)(C,{item:e,index:t,isExpanded:p===t,onToggle:()=>h(p===t?null:t)},t))]})]})]})}},1563,[1,33,70,3,1376,1188,239,1182,1186]);
